Skills.Name: Water Barrier
Skills.Description: Shields DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> of skill user's ATK) of Red Elemental allies (behind self) for 15s. Raises own DEF by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 10s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Shields DMG of Red Elemental allies (behind self). Raises own DEF

Skills.Name: Stunning Waves
Skills.Description:
Inflicts <color=red>{0}%</color> DMG on single enemy.
Further inflicts Stun for 3s.

Skills.Name: Shiny Memory
Skills.Description: Shields DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> of skill user's ATK) of all allies for 15s. Further raises ATK by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 15s if Seven Shadows. Recovers own HP by <color=red>{2}%</color> of ATK.
Skills.ShortDescription: Shields DMG of all allies, raises ATK if Seven Shadows. Recovers own HP

Skills.Name: Strike Combo

Skills.ShortDescription: Reduces DMG Received for all allies, inflicts DMG on single enemy
